dc.title: Congressman Brian Bilbray, California's 50th District - Homepage
dc.description: Brian P. Bilbray represents the 50th Congressional District of California. He currently serves on the House Armed Services Committee, the Veterans'Affairs Committee and the Committee on Government Reform. He brings to his constituency a unique level of experience having served the people of San Diego County as a Mayor, County Supervisor and Congressman. His two decades of business and local government service were instrumental in developing San Diego County's progressive initiatives regarding environmental protection, pollution control and economic development.
